// =============================================================================
// v_2.ino - ESP32 embedded receiver/protection prototype
//
// Based on receiver/python/v_1/v_1.ino + read_from_generator_rms_robust.py.
// The ESP32 now owns the critical path:
//   ADC -> offset/scale -> cycle detection -> Fourier phasors -> protections -> relay outputs.
//
// The firmware does not write oscillography files. Protection results are exposed
// directly on ESP32 GPIOs to drive a 4-channel relay module.
// =============================================================================

